Raptors epic struggle? Imo its not that hard, the tough skin mastery so good too. Worst comes to worst skip it and do scuttle if you have a way to stun it.
You may want to check this out: http://www.reddit.com/r/leagueoflegends/comments/33d3am/dynamic_lich_bane_idea
