Here's an example of a viable build on Warwick using lichbane: {{item:3100}} {{item:3124}} {{item:3146}} {{item:3065}} 
Since Warwick has no cc beyond his ult gunblade's active slow would work well. The lichbane could also be able to spellvamp but only off A protion of the damage like say off of equation #1 worth of the damage and at a 50% reduced effectiveness. That way gunblade will belong more on hybrid champs as I believe it was originally intended to work.
Or get frozen heart mercs and warmogs with
{{item:3116}} {{item:3100}} {{item:3091}}  since he has no cc rylais could work nicely on him.
